{"filter":false,"title":"womens-day-2017.1.php","tooltip":"/events/womens-day-2017.1.php","undoManager":{"mark":4,"position":4,"stack":[[{"start":{"row":55,"column":8},"end":{"row":80,"column":14},"action":"remove","lines":["<div class=\"jumbotron\">","           ","          <p class=\"methodText\"><strong>International Women’s Day</strong> is the day on which we express gratitude to women who have fought and broken all the barriers to reach the pinnacle of success in every sphere of life. This day is very special to them all around the globe.","            </p>","          <p class=\"methodText\">To grace this memorable day, Team Miracle had arranged a special dinner for the ladies at our offshore facilities <strong>Miracle-City cafeteria</strong> and <strong>Miracle-Heights lawn</strong> besides really fun filled activities. Also, the team wished them with beautiful quotes on specially designed greeting cards.","             </p>","         <p class=\"methodText\">It was their time and all the women had gathered for the event. It started with fun activities like Treasure Hunt, Ramp Walk, Dubsmash, Memory Game and it went on with great fun. The lights were on and the DJ was up! Girls couldn’t resist the pumping beats as their power-packed energy rocked the dance floor.","         </p>","         <p class=\"methodText\">Strengthening women in IT as the motive, women from Miracle, in white T-shirts, walked all the way from <strong>YMCA</strong> to <strong>RK beach</strong> early in the morning at <strong>07:00 AM</strong> on <strong>March 11, 2017</strong>. They were very proud and felt honoured to be a part of this great <strong>unity walk</strong>.","         </p>","             ","        <div class=\"row\">","       <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","      ","      <img src=\"../images/events/womens-day2-2017.png\" alt=\"womens-day\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","      ","        </div>","        <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","      ","      <img src=\"../images/events/womens-day3-2017.png\" alt=\"womens-day\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","      ","        </div>","        </div>","     <p class=\"methodText\">Finally, women of <strong>Miracle</strong> were rejoiced with all the fun and activities held at the event and felt special for being their kind. Miracle had a great time recognising the power of women and took immense joy in wishing a happy <strong>International Women’s Day!</strong>","           </p> ","        </div>"]}],[{"start":{"row":55,"column":8},"end":{"row":87,"column":10},"action":"insert","lines":["<div class=\"jumbotron\">","           ","           <p class=\"methodText\">Valentine’s day is a very special day that spreads expression of love to the loved ones. The boldness of the red roses and the sweetness of the loving hearts mesmerized the Miraclites. Where luxurious gifts, diamonds and jewels fade away, a single rose can express millions of feelings. The most easiest thing that can done without any limitations and boundaries is caring. It’s impossible to buy a loving heart, so try to win it by sharing your love and charm with the people around you.","</p>","          <p class=\"methodText\">","To lighten up love and helping the poor as a initiative, an event <strong>“Spread Your Love”</strong> was organized on the occasion of <strong>Valentine’s Day</strong>. The employees gathered at the lobby, picked a rose and a chit from the love box and two lovely people were declared as Mr and Ms. Valentine of the year.</p>","         <p class=\"methodText\">","         The lucky valentine’s were,","         </p>","        <div class=\"row\">","       <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","      <img src=\"../images/events/Mr.Valentine-2017.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","      <br>","      <img src=\"../images/events/Ms.valentain2.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","       <h5 class=\"heavy\">Miracle City:</h5>","           <p class=\"methodText\">Mr. Valentine - Gurvinder Singh (Development)</p>","           <p class=\"methodText\">Ms. Valentine - Sarada Tatisetti (Hubble Team)</p>","        </div>","        <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","        <img src=\"../images/events/Mr.valentine3.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","        <br>","        <img src=\"../images/events/Bhavani.png\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","           <h5 class=\"heavy\">Miracle Heights :</h5>","        <p class=\"methodText\">Mr. Valentine - Pavan Kumar Midathana (HR Team)</p>","        <p class=\"methodText\">Ms. Valentine - Bhavani Vanapalli (Recruitment)</p>","        </div>","        </div>","        ","        ","         ","<p class=\"methodText\">Miraclites never failed to glaze out their care and warmth towards people. A great idea for spreading love made Miraclites, buy the roses for a good cause. The amount of 8000 INR was collected, which will be spent for a charity event as a token of love. They enjoyed each and every moment of the lovely event with happiness and love around.","</p>","    </div>"],"id":3}],[{"start":{"row":46,"column":35},"end":{"row":46,"column":45},"action":"remove","lines":["Womens Day"],"id":4},{"start":{"row":46,"column":35},"end":{"row":46,"column":50},"action":"insert","lines":["Valentine’s Day"]}],[{"start":{"row":40,"column":30},"end":{"row":40,"column":47},"action":"remove","lines":["Womens Day | 2017"],"id":5},{"start":{"row":40,"column":30},"end":{"row":40,"column":51},"action":"insert","lines":["Valentines Day | 2017"]}],[{"start":{"row":7,"column":11},"end":{"row":7,"column":28},"action":"remove","lines":["Womens Day | 2017"],"id":6},{"start":{"row":7,"column":11},"end":{"row":7,"column":32},"action":"insert","lines":["Valentines Day | 2017"]}]]},"ace":{"folds":[],"scrolltop":0,"scrollleft":0,"selection":{"start":{"row":7,"column":32},"end":{"row":7,"column":32},"isBackwards":false},"options":{"guessTabSize":true,"useWrapMode":false,"wrapToView":true},"firstLineState":0},"timestamp":1489604753996,"hash":"74c208717850f0b067591002493775b05e09045c"}